  <brief_title>SUV Max as Predictor of Outcome in Cervical Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Evaluate the Value of SUV-Max in PET-FDG in Predicting Outcome of Surgery Vis a Vis Need for Radiotherapy</official_title>
